{"tid":1910230,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"唔想立法會選舉無得投票？ 唔該入黎","createTime":"2020-03-04T13:45:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-26T09:01:42.000Z","uid":235324,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"80cca5838682289d6ef333da9648f985009d987e","tid":1910230,"uid":235324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T13:45:17.000Z","msg":"話說之前有個電話打過黎 但我果陣番緊工聽唔到。 之後打番過去，先知原來係選舉事務處打黎 話寄信比我無回 問我做乜唔回 係咪轉左地址等等。<br />\n<br />\n假設你收唔到信，佢打比你而你無聽電話 又或者佢打唔到比你，你好大機會去到投票果日先會知自己原來已經被DQ<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我建議大家如果無收過信/唔肯定，可以email/打去問下 大家既每一票都好重要。<br />\n<br />\n下面係我同個職員傾完電話之後，佢Email比我既內容，寫到明 我唔覆既話隨時會被取消投票資格。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RUToOBu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRUToOBu.png&h=7dd7dc41&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"242886bfccdb6ee069bb8caf707fd164812744e5","tid":1910230,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T13:46:42.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n<br />\n到底大家撐唔撐港台<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1909951\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1909951</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a972a5a7334c218e50b55cb2fdad0dafca33fd6c","tid":1910230,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T14:32:21.000Z","msg":"【夠鐘上Twitter啦喂！】大量英美議員需要人推！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1910266\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1910266</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">夠鐘做野啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大量議員tweet唔夠人</span></span>"},{"pid":"b5accc115bfd3cf576fd76d57bdd6466654e9b66","tid":1910230,"uid":235324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T17:12:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a50f3fad7450109f7249eb701ded475573c5977a